      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 4,
      "message": "Hi Mandeep,\nIn the helm charts, lots of places points to this /dockerdata-nfs. And they are hardcoded. \n\nTo avoid config error, I will keep this path as it is now. If needed, I will parameterize that path.\n\nFor exaple:\nhttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/gitweb?p=oom.git;a=blob;f=kubernetes/sdnc/templates/nfs-provisoner-deployment.yaml;h=a283d0f626c3a9cbebe84fe88bf5c10872ec94d9;hb=HEAD\n  51       volumes:\n  52         - name: export-volume\n  53           hostPath:\n  54             path: /dockerdata-nfs/{{ .Values.nsPrefix }}/sdnc/data",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 505,
        "name": "Jun (Nicolas) Hu",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "jun.nicolas.hu@att.com",
        "username": "jh245g"
